metadata.name: Symbolism Hidden At Night
metadata.description: A collaboration with Manolo Sierra. This work juxtaposes Manolo's 1999 oil painting "¿dónde está el simbolismo?" with his 2005 oil painting "La nit del Matadero", bringing to life the feeling of the former whilst retaining the prepotence of the latter, in a new work which exists nowhere in the physical world.
